snippet.title: Ghostbusters: Spirits Unleashed DLC #3 Teaser
snippet.description:
DLC 3 is here and it's FREE! We just got a call for our next job! Strap on your dancing shoes and Ghostbusting gear as we venture into the New Motion Club! But watch out for the new Watcher Ghost Type! It’s safe to assume that before you ever notice a Watcher, it’s certainly already noticed you. 

Get all the details here:
https://www.ghostbusterssu.com/news/

Ghostbusters: Spirits Unleashed is available on PC on EPIC GAMES, PS4™, PS4™Pro, PS5™, Xbox Series X|S and Xbox One. To learn more about the game visit: https://www.ghostbusterssu.com/

Want to get the latest news on the game OR to meet up with other players in the community? Join us using these links!
